  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dca.\u0d86\u0dbb\u0dca. \u0d9a\u0dda\u0dad\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0daf\u0ddd\u0dc2\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel Q.R. Balagiri error to code",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Q.R. related to the 'National Fuel Licence' implemented by the Ministry of Energy. Power and Energy Minister Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera says that the implementation of the code has been postponed until the 1st of August.",
        "From the 1st of August, Q.R. Fuel will be released according to the code and the last digit of the number plate and the National Youth Corps, National Youth Council members and volunteers will report to Q.R. in the next 10 days. The minister also said that he supports the implementation of the code system at petrol stations.",
        "Energy Minister Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera has said on several occasions that this program will be implemented covering the entire country from a few weeks but it has not been implemented till now and the minister lastly said that it will be implemented from today (25)."
      ],
